➜realme 真我 V5 体验：千元 5G 闪充手机，能有多「奥利给」？
https://www.ifanr.com/1356227?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	8210
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356351" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01_meitu_1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01_meitu_1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01_meitu_1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01_meitu_1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01_meitu_1-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>1998 年，当周华健的《我是谁》副歌部分第一次出现「奥利给」的时候，没有人注意到这句科萨部落语言。</p>
<p>20 年后，当「冬泳怪鸽」把「奥利给」当作口头禅，给自己和屏幕前的我们加油打气时，这句话才真正被大家认识。</p>
<p>作为「冬泳怪鸽」的铁粉，当我看到熟悉的「奥利给」成为 realme 真我 V5 手机的代名词时，引起了我的好奇：「手机怎么能奥利给呢？」</p>
<p>拿到真我 V5 之后，包装盒上的银色腰带立刻吸引了我的注意。「3 分钟闪充，奥利给！」「电量总比困难多」的宣传标语，似乎在疯狂炫耀手机的闪充及续航的能力。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356262" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05873-01.jpg" alt="" width="3999" height="5999" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05873-01.jpg 3999w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05873-01-360x540.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05873-01-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05873-01-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 3999px) 100vw, 3999px" /></p>
<p>这与其在 8 月 3 日的发布会上，被宣传的重点一样。5000 毫安超大电池、30 W 智慧闪充，为这部手机赋予了「奥利给」的资本。不过实际用起来，它真的有那么「奥利给」吗？抱着这个疑问，我开始了体验。</p>
<h3>潮玩设计，吸睛力十足</h3>
<p>首先比较吸睛的，是手机的外观。后背「LOGO Design」搭配上超级镀膜光学工艺和第二代 AG 效果，让手机看上去潮酷年轻。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356263" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01-1.jpg" alt="" width="5594" height="3729" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01-1.jpg 5594w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05894-01-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5594px) 100vw, 5594px" /></p>
<p>需要注意的是，真我 V5 的后盖材质不是 AG 玻璃，而是在塑料材质上，实现了 AG 效果。如果只看不摸的话，质感的确很像玻璃，晶莹感十足。</p>
<p>与 AG 玻璃相比，真我 V5 的背壳没那么滑。上手有种细微的磨砂感，可以稳贴在手掌中。并且塑料材没有玻璃的「冰冷感」，亲肤性强一些。不过缺点也比较明显，就是真我  V5 的背壳容易粘上指纹，吸附的油污很难用干纸巾擦除，需要用上湿纸巾。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356261" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05872-02-01-1.jpg" alt="" width="5894" height="3929" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05872-02-01-1.jpg 5894w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05872-02-01-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05872-02-01-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05872-02-01-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5894px) 100vw, 5894px" /></p>
<p>正面来看，这块 6.5 英寸 LCD 显示屏的显示效果不俗。分辨率为 2400 × 1080，支持 90Hz 刷新率。在日常使用中，无论是刷微博还是打游戏，都感觉非常爽滑。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356264" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05889-01.jpg" alt="" width="5845" height="3896" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05889-01.jpg 5845w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05889-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05889-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05889-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5845px) 100vw, 5845px" /></p>
<p>前置摄像头采用了熟悉的单孔设计，在息屏时，正面看上去一体性非常高。不过在亮屏状态下，手机的「下巴」看起来就略宽了一些。</p>
<p>机身右侧设置了一个指纹电源键，指纹识别的速度非常快，几乎是零延迟解锁。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356265" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05891-01.jpg" alt="" width="5924" height="3950" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05891-01.jpg 5924w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05891-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05891-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05891-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5924px) 100vw, 5924px" /></p>
<p>音量加减键和 SIM 卡槽放在了机身左侧，按键手感偏紧实。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356266" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05893-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05893-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05893-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05893-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05893-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>机身底部集成了 3.5mm 耳机孔、麦克风、Type-C 接口、扬声器。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356267" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05901-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05901-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05901-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05901-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05901-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>不吐不快的是，机身自带的原厂贴膜有点厚，手感很一般。在边缘处做手势动作时，有点硌手。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356270" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05912-01-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05912-01-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05912-01-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05912-01-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05912-01-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<h3>不做花瓶，战斗力出色</h3>
<p>除了外观漂亮，真我 V5 的性能也「拿的出手」。</p>
<p>真我 V5 搭载的是联发科新款集成式 5G 芯片——天玑 720，采用台积电 7nm 制程工艺，支持 5G+4G 双卡双待。实际使用中，5G 信号的稳定性不错，我在广州乘 APM 线时，没有出现过降到 4G 的情景。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356268" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05909-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05909-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05909-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05909-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05909-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>关于天玑 720，一开始我对这颗芯片的性能有所质疑。安安兔 CPU 的跑分为 92884 分，整机的跑分为 287174 分，看起来没有什么亮点。在体验过程中，微博、微信等轻体量应用，自是毫无压力。不过在玩王者荣耀时，整机的流畅性、屏幕的响应度，还是超出了我的想象，全程帧率稳定在 60fps 左右，体验非常顺滑。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356277" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HwVideoEditor_2020_08_02_225247.gif" alt="" width="640" height="360" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HwVideoEditor_2020_08_02_225247.gif 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/HwVideoEditor_2020_08_02_225247-360x203.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>值得一提的是，这颗芯片的发热量控制地非常优秀，我连玩半个小时的王者荣耀后，机身的温度并没有明显的上升。</p>
<p>后置摄像头采用四摄矩阵摄像模组，4800 万主摄 + 119°超广角镜头 + 4cm 超级微距镜头+黑白人像镜头的组合。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356269" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05898-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05898-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05898-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05898-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05898-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在使用过程中，相机的响应度、操控性等方面表现都不错。成片的色彩上比较讨喜，接近真实。不过锐度有些高，像是算法为了提高清晰度而有意为之，显得有些刻意。<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356271" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155745.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155745.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155745-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155745-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155745-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 1x 主摄镜头</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356273" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155752.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155752.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155752-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155752-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155752-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 2x 放大</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356272" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155748.jpg" alt="" width="3264" height="2448" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155748.jpg 3264w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155748-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155748-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200803155748-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 广角镜头</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356274" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200731194603.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200731194603.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200731194603-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200731194603-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG20200731194603-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 广角镜头（夜景）</p>
</div>
<h3>闪充加持，续航奥利给！</h3>
<p>超长续航是 realme 真我 V5 让我印象最深刻的特点，这是 realme 首次推出 5000 毫安超大容量的手机。</p>
<p>「饭量大的同时，吃的也快。」真我 V5 标配了 30W 智慧闪充。不仅充电快，还具备过温保护、过充保护、过压和过流保护等防护措施。值得一提的是，电源适配器的充电口，与电源线的充电口，内部都用了与包装盒同样的橘黄色，细节拉满，看上去很漂亮。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356276" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05879-01.jpg" alt="" width="5713" height="3816" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05879-01.jpg 5713w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05879-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05879-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05879-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5713px) 100vw, 5713px" /></p>
<p>拿到手机后，我为了将其电量耗尽，方便测试闪充性能，着实费了很大功夫。基本上每跑一次安安兔的测试（大约 9 分 54 秒），只能掉 2% 的电。</p>
<p>在电量终于耗尽后，我对它进行了「魔鬼测试」。既然它「腰带」上写着「三分钟闪充，奥利给！」我就试试只给它充电三分钟，能用多久。</p>
<p>我用秒表计时，用标配的 30W 充电器给真我 V5 充电，3 分钟从电量不足以开机的情况充到了 7%。</p>
<p>在不开启省电模式的情况下，我带着它出门了。在此期间，我用手机刷了大约 5 分钟的朋友圈和微博、拍了 11 张照片、用了 25 分钟的导航，最后在下载一款 App 的过程中，没电自动关机了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356352" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot_2020-08-02-13-38-47-11.jpg" alt="" width="2160" height="2400" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot_2020-08-02-13-38-47-11.jpg 2160w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot_2020-08-02-13-38-47-11-360x400.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot_2020-08-02-13-38-47-11-768x853.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Screenshot_2020-08-02-13-38-47-11-922x1024.jpg 922w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /></p>
<p>13:38 充完电出门，一直到 14:39 没电关机。中间的一个小时，手机的亮屏时间在 30 分钟左右，其余时间均为息屏待机。充电 3 分钟的续航令我满意，足够极端情况下应急。</p>
<p>晚间我又按照上述条件测试了一下，3 分钟充到 7% 之后，打了一局王者荣耀后（对局时间为 11 分 34 秒），手机剩余电量 5%，整体功耗较低。</p>
<p>在充电速度上，真我 V5 标配的 30W 充电器，充电的效率比较均衡。55 分钟可以将电量从 5% 充到 100%。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356278" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhggf.png" alt="" width="2132" height="1596" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhggf.png 2132w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhggf-360x269.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhggf-768x575.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhggf-1024x767.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2132px) 100vw, 2132px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 充电时间与充电效率一览</p>
</div>
<p>在电量达到 80% 前，基本上每分钟可以充 2% 的电。达到 80% 后速度放缓，基本上每两分钟充 3% 的电。整体充电速度可以列在第一阵营中。</p>
<p>对于年轻人而言，除了 5G、闪充、高刷屏、长续航、外观美等条件，购机时还要考虑价格是否合适。</p>
<p>真我 V5 的售价也比较贴合年轻人。6+128GB 版本首发优惠价仅 1399 元；8+128GB 版本 1899 元。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356279" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05885-01.jpg" alt="" width="5892" height="3928" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05885-01.jpg 5892w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05885-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05885-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05885-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5892px) 100vw, 5892px" /></p>
<p>当代年轻人，比如我，不仅有「花呗焦虑」，还有「续航焦虑」。当我手机的电量低于 30%，并且身边没有充电线和充电宝时，就会变成「热锅上的蚂蚁」。</p>
<p>在体验真我 V5 的过程中，这种「续航焦虑」被打破了。只要手机充满电，即便不带充电宝，也能安心出门「浪」一整天。而 1399 元的首发价，也能打消我的「花呗焦虑」。</p>
<p>在争抢千元档市场的路上，各家手机厂商都在使出全身解数，来提高产品的性价比。对于消费者来说，这无疑是一件好事。也期待未来能看到越来越多的「真我 V5」，出现大众视野中。</p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/wanghelong" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
<div style="padding:10px 10px 10px 0">
<div style="margin:0;font-size: 14px;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/wanghelong" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;">换新言 (换新言)</a></strong>
</div>
