➜vivo S7 图赏：这可能是目前最轻薄的 5G 手机
https://www.ifanr.com/1356453?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	41938
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356471" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05962-01-01_meitu_2.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05962-01-01_meitu_2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05962-01-01_meitu_2-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05962-01-01_meitu_2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05962-01-01_meitu_2-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>人是一种奇怪的生物。当某种现象越来越多，直至成为常态的时候，我们就会认为它是理所应当的，即便我们并不喜欢。</p>
<p>随着 5G、高刷屏等配置的普及，手机们为了保持续航能力，开始在重量与体积上妥协。当妥协的姿态越来越多，我们逐渐觉得 190g+、甚至 200g+ 的手机很正常，或许手机本来就应该是这样。</p>
<p>这次拿到 vivo s7 之后，一种熟悉的感觉回来了，似乎回到了高中时，手机屏幕还不大，手机重量被控制的还很好的时代。因为 S7 实在太轻了，只有 170g，配合上 7.39 毫米厚的机身，说它是目前最轻薄的 5G 手机之一并不为过。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356455" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG_0733-2.gif" alt="" width="800" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG_0733-2.gif 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG_0733-2-360x203.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/IMG_0733-2-768x432.gif 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>首先包装盒上若有若无的「S」，随着角度的变换会有一种流动感，设计的很漂亮。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356459" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05956-01.jpg" alt="" width="1289" height="865" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05956-01.jpg 1289w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05956-01-360x242.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05956-01-768x515.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05956-01-1024x687.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1289px) 100vw, 1289px" /></p>
<p>vivo S7 共有三种颜色：莫奈漫彩、爵士黑和月光白。我个人更喜欢月光白一些，整体看上去更轻盈，在光影下显得十分通透。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356456" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05966-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05966-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05966-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05966-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05966-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>手机的背面采用了熟悉的 AG 磨砂工艺。配合上月光白，观感上有点像月光下的迷雾，或者说像一块玉石。</p>
<p>左下方是银色的 Logo，看起来比较协调，没有破坏整体的美感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356458" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05988-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05988-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05988-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05988-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05988-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>摄像头模组的设计，看起来与其大哥 vivo X50 Pro 的排列方式一样，都是「阶梯式摄像头设计」。模组的边缘有倒角抛光设计，提升了精致感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356460" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05977-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05977-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05977-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05977-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05977-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>主摄是一颗 6400 万像素的摄像头，下面两个分别是 800 万超广角微距镜头和 200 万艺术风格黑白镜头。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05982-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05982-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05982-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05982-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05982-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>我尝试用主摄拍了一下照片，无论是质感还是细节，都令人满意。不过看起来略微有些偏冷，也有可能是屏幕调教的原因。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356462" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05990-01.jpg" alt="" width="1560" height="1041" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05990-01.jpg 1560w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05990-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05990-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05990-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1560px) 100vw, 1560px" /></p>
<p>轻薄的机身握持感很好，单手持机并不会觉得累。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356457" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05949-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05949-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05949-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05949-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05949-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>S7 的前脸采用了刘海屏的设计，屏幕尺寸为 6.44 英寸，分辨率为 2400 × 1080 像素，ppi 达到了 408，不过没有 90Hz 高刷屏有些遗憾，这应该是出于和 X 系列作区隔的考虑。<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356463" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06010-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06010-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06010-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06010-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06010-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>屏幕峰值亮度 600nit，覆盖 DCI-P3 色域，支持 HDR 显示，整体上观感不错。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356464" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05995-01.jpg" alt="" width="1484" height="992" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05995-01.jpg 1484w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05995-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05995-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05995-01-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px" /></p>
<p>作为一款主打自拍的手机，vivo S7 的前置摄像头比较有看头。主摄是三星 GH1，4400 万像素，最大光圈 f2.0，支持相位对焦，副摄为 105° 超广角镜头，800 万像素。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356465" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06000-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06000-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06000-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06000-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06000-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>vivo S7 前置自拍支持 4K/60fps 视频录制和人像防抖技术，且支持 4K 录像模式下的美颜功能。这对于喜欢拍 vlog 的人群来说很有吸引力。</p>
<p>有意思的是，我拿到 vivo S7 的一瞬间，还以为边框是金属材质的。因为无论是看上去还是摸上去，塑料感都很弱。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356466" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhhv.png" alt="" width="2890" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhhv.png 2890w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhhv-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhhv-768x514.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hhhv-1024x686.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2890px) 100vw, 2890px" /></p>
<p>音量加减键与电源键整合到了机身右侧。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356467" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05964-01.jpg" alt="" width="1596" height="1066" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05964-01.jpg 1596w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05964-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05964-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC05964-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1596px) 100vw, 1596px" /></p>
<p>机身下方集合了 SIM 卡槽、麦克风、Type-C 接口和扬声器。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356468" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hsghdw.png" alt="" width="2890" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hsghdw.png 2890w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hsghdw-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hsghdw-768x514.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hsghdw-1024x686.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2890px) 100vw, 2890px" /></p>
<p>手机标配的是一枚 33W 的充电器，支持 vivo 2.0 闪充。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356469" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jhjqwh.png" alt="" width="2890" height="1936" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jhjqwh.png 2890w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jhjqwh-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jhjqwh-768x514.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jhjqwh-1024x686.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2890px) 100vw, 2890px" /></p>
<p>总体来说，vivo S7 让我印象最深刻的是它的轻薄，毕竟我已经很久没有用过 180g 以下的手机了。其次它的颜值让我也很喜欢。月光白的配色，实际上手要比照片看起来更有质感一些。</p>
<p>vivo S7 的目标人群很明确，就是喜欢自拍的用户。因此它在前置摄像头上下了不少功夫。此外，对于经常自拍的人来说，相信举着 190g+ 的手机，胳膊很快就能体会到「酸爽」的感觉。vivo S7 170g 的重量，对胳膊和手腕就友好多了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356470" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06005-01.jpg" alt="" width="1616" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06005-01.jpg 1616w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06005-01-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06005-01-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06005-01-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" /></p>
<p>不过熊掌与鱼不可兼得，vivo S7 的定位让其只采用了高通骁龙 765G 处理器，日常使用没什么问题，但在游戏方面，表现难以出众。</p>
<p>价格上，8GB+128GB 版本售价 2798 元、8GB+256GB 售价 3098 元。不过甲之砒霜，乙之蜜糖嘛。性价比如何，就看使用者的主要用途是什么了。</p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/wanghelong" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
<div style="padding:10px 10px 10px 0">
